dublin_core.dcvalue: MAMA Global hosted an in country learning workshop in Timor Leste in collaboration with Health Alliance International HAI and their technical partner Catalpa International shared lessons learned best practices and led site visits focus groups and community outreach activities Workshop attendees also presented on their own programs highlighting lessons learned successes challenges and how they have adapted the MAMA messages and model for their own unique contexts
MAMA in Country Learning Workshop: Key Take-Aways from Timor-Leste
